The paper is about an open-source Python package developed for interpreting deep models, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Specifically, the paper focuses on deep neural networks, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
